headline: MSCI (MSCI) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of investment analytics provider MSCI (NYSE:MSCI) jumped 3.1% in the afternoon session after analyst firm JP Morgan set a price target of $655.00, implying a potential 16.30% upside within 12 months.
